name: TamaT - Aggressive Digital IDK
description:
The electronic music activity unit from Surabaya "TamaT" released their first single entitled Aggressive Digital Idk, responding to a dilapidated system that will always be repeated until our children and grandchildren, Responding to criminals as criminals without any consequences and adding to the environment hanging around, responding to the ignorance of one of the personnel how to making eKTP, and cursing all programmers who deal with expensive results in shambles. 1 track they launched under the auspices of Anti Trust Record, an electronic music label that is starting to rebuild its image as a record label, not as a party thrower.
Tamat is a project initiated by Eri (Hi Mom! and reveur) with andhika (Karga) and Samson (koteka is the reason) in early 2019 to create a digital hardcore band, hopefully this will be Eri's last project after always on hiatus with other bands. his previous band because he was left wandering. As a preheat before ep. TamaT was released, they made 1 full gass track before their band format was shown. Finally, they took one of the new personnel, August.
This track is not promoting someone, but appreciating something that we think fits in our mind. enjoy in your room.
